All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AddLocationToAddVehicleActivity
AddLocationToAddVehicleActivity is for users to confirm a location to associate with their vehicle.
AddVehicleActivity
AddVehicleActivity is for users to register their vehicles to the Firebase Firestore.
CarpoolFragment
CarpoolFragment is a Fragment that controls the carpool page.
ElectricVehicle
ElectricVehicle is a child class of Vehicle to instantiate the kiloCarbonSavedPerRidePerKm variable.
EntryActivity
EntryActivity is for users to register/login through the email and password or Google-Sign-In protocols provided through Firebase Authentication.
FuelVehicle
FuelVehicle is a child class of Vehicle to instantiate the kiloCarbonSavedPerRidePerKm variable.
GPSHelper
GPSHelper is a helper class to get the current location of the user.
HybridVehicle
HybridVehicle is a child class of Vehicle to instantiate the kiloCarbonSavedPerRidePerKm variable.
LeaderboardAdapter
LeaderboardAdapter extends RecyclerView.Adapter to format data from Firebase Firestore into a RecyclerView for LeaderboardFragment
LeaderboardCallback
LeaderboardCallback is an interface to wait for Firebase Firestore response for the LeaderboardFragment
LeaderboardFragment
LeaderboardFragment is a Fragment that controls the leaderboard page.
LoginActivity
LoginActivity is for users to login through the email and password protocols provided through Firebase Authentication.
MainViewActivity
MainViewActivity is the main intractable activity to access the person, carpool, and leaderboard pages.
PersonFragment
PersonFragment is a Fragment that controls the person page.
RegisterActivity
RegisterActivity is for users to register through the email and password protocols provided through Firebase Authentication.
RidesAdapter
RidesAdapter extends RecyclerView.Adapter to format data from Firebase Firestore into a RecyclerView for CarpoolFragment
RidesListCallback
RidesListCallback is an interface to wait for Firebase Firestore response for the CarpoolFragment
User
User is a class to represent a user's relevant information.
Vehicle
Vehicle is a class to represent a vehicle's relevant information.
VehicleOwnerNameCallback
VehicleOwnerNameCallback is an interface to wait for Firebase Firestore response for the RidesAdapter
VehicleSchoolMapsFragment
VehicleSchoolMapsFragment is a Fragment that shows CIS and the vehicle position.
